      "span_text": "RNA was extracted using the RNeasy Plus Micro kit (Qiagen, Valencia, CA, USA) according to the manufacturer's protocol. Concentration of isolated RNA was measured using a Nanodrop 2000 spectrophotometer (Thermo Fisher Scientific, Waltham, MA, USA). After RNA isolation, cDNA was synthesized using Ready-To-Go You-Prime First-Strand beads (GE Healthcare Bio-Sciences, Pittsburgh, PA, USA) as previously reported. [CITATION_1]"
